trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers by <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller värden som ska användas som identifierare av <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: Dessa identifierare som används av UI Automation-providers.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.
trans-unit.target: En UI Automation klientprogram ska använda motsvarande fält i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>

trans-unit.source: Identifies the event raised when an item is added to a collection of selected items.
trans-unit.target: Identifierar den händelse som aktiveras när ett objekt läggs till i en samling för de valda objekten.

trans-unit.source: If the result of an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A> call is a single selected item, then an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent> must be raised instead.
trans-unit.target: Om resultatet av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A>anropet är en enskild post, och sedan en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent>måste ökas i stället.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A>

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: Den här identifieraren används av UI Automation-providers.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.
trans-unit.target: En UI Automation klientprogram ska använda det motsvarande fältet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the event raised when an item is removed from a collection of selected items.
trans-unit.target: Identifierar den händelse som aktiveras när ett objekt tas bort från en samling för de valda objekten.

trans-unit.source: If the result of a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A> call is a single selected item, then an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent> will be raised instead.
trans-unit.target: Om resultatet av en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A>anropet är en enskild post, och sedan en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent>aktiveras i stället.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementSelectedEvent> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A>

trans-unit.source: This identifier is used by UI Automation providers.
trans-unit.target: Den här identifieraren används av UI Automation-providers.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent field in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.
trans-unit.target: En UI Automation klientprogram ska använda det motsvarande fältet i <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPattern>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Identifies the event that is raised when a single item is selected (causing all previously selected items to become deselected).
trans-unit.target: Identifierar händelsen som utlöses när ett objekt väljs (och alla tidigare valda objekt till blir avmarkeras).

trans-unit.source: If the result of either an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A> or a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A> call is more than one selected item, then an <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementAddedToSelectionEvent> or <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementRemovedFromSelectionEvent> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: Om resultatet av antingen en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A>eller en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A>anrop mer än ett objekt har valts, och sedan en <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementAddedToSelectionEvent>eller <xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementRemovedFromSelectionEvent>händelsen utlöses.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementRemovedFromSelectionEvent> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.SelectionItemPatternIdentifiers.ElementAddedToSelectionEvent> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.RemoveFromSelection%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Provider.ISelectionItemProvider.AddToSelection%2A>
